{"tid":1691143,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「請入」關於黃埔區吹雞永遠唔夠人一事","createTime":"2019-11-03T14:05:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T18:13:50.000Z","uid":320191,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"c2daf66637a58085d8b417167122c4e13b5be0e2","tid":1691143,"uid":320191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:05:52.000Z","msg":"「黃埔區每次吹雞都得數人出現,永遠快閃搞唔成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就似今日咁,本來八點吹雞,等左個半鐘都唔撚見人,一個二個話落但又隱形左咁,撚到好多人又灰又嬲,唔再信藍埔,仲不如去其他區好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\n我覺得黃埔吹雞之所以失敗,一係因為太突發,一黎就玩快閃,不得不承認其實黄埔肯做野既人數極少,加上大部分居民屬中產中年,和理非居多,同埋而家成個香港係少左人敢出,所以黃埔咁撚失敗既原因係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">吹雞太突發</span></span>同埋<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">文宣不足</span></span><br />\n<br />\n一來其實唔多人有用tg,尤其堆中年,唔好見公海有4000幾人,其實mon 夠同區外人多,真正黃埔啲手足未必知有咩行動同幾時要人<br />\n<br />\n我覺得不如搞番個和理非商場活動吸引人數先,似之前咁都有150-200人,和理唱又好,人鏈又好,吸到有一定人數,足以掩護到其他手足快閃行動,<br />\n比起下下突發吹雞好好多<br />\n而且要做足文宣,係fb網上預早一星期吹雞效果最好<br />\n<br />\n我見好多黃埔手足好以下下比人狼來了咁款,不斷惡性循環冇好結果,希望我既建議有用<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港,時代革命!</span></span><br />\n<br />\nps<span style=\"color: purple;\">各位真係咪再係公海講自己位置同組隊,真心好多mon狗</span>"},{"pid":"4e057b8769908611660469b55d80bcdddfd2b4c6","tid":1691143,"uid":125542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:10:23.000Z","msg":"藍埔"},{"pid":"2c0e720a5e21a5fc8907a8fb47946e8a273a3ca9","tid":1691143,"uid":302582,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:11:09.000Z","msg":"真係次次都唔夠人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e42d3c206d93aa3ab7198bd2130424a3a5d44df3","tid":1691143,"uid":266820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:11:13.000Z","msg":"好多附近人都去左其他區 之後街坊黎到又見唔到人唔知邊到等相認唔到 之後就造成左大家翻屋企聚唔到人嘅狀況"},{"pid":"0e2c97901ca00fd02deea0d605af2ad1f6fe85b4","tid":1691143,"uid":267128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:12:09.000Z","msg":"黃埔街坊入一入嚟"},{"pid":"f75fb9a48758ea8b03de4f708753361d617dddd0","tid":1691143,"uid":320191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e42d3c206d93aa3ab7198bd2130424a3a5d44df3","tid":1691143,"uid":266820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:11:13.000Z","msg":"好多附近人都去左其他區 之後街坊黎到又見唔到人唔知邊到等相認唔到 之後就造成左大家翻屋企聚唔到人嘅狀況"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:12:58.000Z","msg":"因為原及冇講定有活動,又突然吹雞,所以好難聚人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ebac824987c45aa308a3873606c786dc498a5d3","tid":1691143,"uid":195690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:18:19.000Z","msg":"Push (1/10)"},{"pid":"adfece8ccd74ee05e2e9c85a9a3cdfb6de903ee8","tid":1691143,"uid":195690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:18:30.000Z","msg":"Push (2/10)"},{"pid":"a4e20f6d31da724d2f7700f245e9384404aed8d0","tid":1691143,"uid":195690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:18:42.000Z","msg":"Push (3/10)"},{"pid":"08e4c7df63f6b3ab38df20423957bd80707ac102","tid":1691143,"uid":195690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:19:02.000Z","msg":"Push (4/10)"},{"pid":"8d3e722f31645f8b2143ce574daac3e04af63dcd","tid":1691143,"uid":195690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:19:14.000Z","msg":"Push (5/10)"},{"pid":"851819c0c04458096ce212f79ee3e06d3cfe066c","tid":1691143,"uid":320191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ebac824987c45aa308a3873606c786dc498a5d3","tid":1691143,"uid":195690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:18:19.000Z","msg":"Push (1/10)"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:19:29.000Z","msg":"多謝手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我p牌推唔